quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  39,6,"Joomi mon, onon …ìee yim…ìe, tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, ndun woni Aadama. Refti O tagi e makko, genndo makko on Hawaa. O tagani on geloo…ói e na'i e dammi e be'i, nooneeji jeetati, noone kala, gorel e deyel. Himo tagira on ka teege yumma mon en, sagara na…ìi sagara, e nder ni…ìe reedu e rennga e jowtol. Ko On moo…óon tagoowo …óum fow, woni Allah, Joomi mon. Ko Kanko laamu woodani. Rewetee…óo e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno ferlitora…óon e rewugol ko tagataa, acca …óon tagoowo On?"
  39,7,"Si onon …ìee yim…ìe, on yeddii Joomi mon, anndon tun, Allah ko yondinii…óo e gom…óinal mon, keeferaaku mon, lorrataa Mo. Ko onon …óum lorrata, tawde Allah kan, O siforaali yamiroowo pankere e ko a√±inii. Si on yettii Mo non e neemaaji Makko …óin, on gom…óinii Mo, O weltanto on, O warjoo on e …óum. Anndon wonii bakkondinki woo, ronndantaako wokki goo. Kala e ko faggitanii hoore mun. Refti ko ka Joomi mon tun, woni ruttorde mon, √ëalnde Darngal; O yeetitoo on, fii ko gollayno…óon aduna, O yo…ìita on, njo…ìdi golle mon …óen. Kanko senii…óo On, pellet, ko O anndu…óo ko woni e …ìer…óe jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Huunde e ko woni e majje, suu…óaaki Mo."
  39,8,"Si lorra he…ìii yeddu…óo, wono √±awu maa sattireede arsike maa hulugol yoolaade, o toroo nde Joomi makko hunciranta mo …óum, ruttagol e Makko, Kanko tun. Refti non, si Allah neeminirii mo huncangol mo on lorra, o yejjita fii Allah, Mo O torotonoo On, ado …óum. O wa…óana Mo kafidii…ói, rewetee…ói, ko wanaa Allah, no o majjinira wo…ó…ìe goo, e laawol Allah ngol. Nulaa…óo, maakan sugu on …óon : dakmitor yeddugol maa ngol, yeru ko o heddori…óaa e duu…ìi kon. Anndaa pellet, ko a jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe duumoytoo…ìe ka Yiite …ìen, √ëalnde Darngal."
  39,9,"Kaa ko on …óoftii…óo Allah, fe∆¥∆¥iniroowo jemma on, sujjangol Mo, darorana Mo naafe, hara himo huli lepte laakara …óen, himo jortrii yurmeende Joomi makko nden, kaa ko yeddu…óo rewoowo Allah on ka sa…óteende tun, o yedda Mo ka hoyeende, o wa…óana Mo kafidii…ói? An Nulaa…óo, maaku : Hara …ìen anndu…ìe ko Allah farli kon e ma…ì…ìe, hino fota e …ìen …ìe anndaa huunde e …óum? Anndu ko taskotoo kon ko senndi …óin feddeeji …ói…ói, ko joomiraa…ìe haqqille hisu…óe …óen."
  39,10,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan jeyaa…ìe Am gom…óim…ìe Lam Min e Nulaa…ìe Am …ìen: huliree Joomi mon, …óoftagol yamaruyeeji Makko, e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko. Hino woodani mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe golle …ìen e mon aduna, mo∆¥∆¥oreede e mun aduna, walleede e cellal e jawdi, ka laakara, hara ko Aljanna. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi, feree e mayri, haa e nokku ka waawoton rewude Mo woo, ka go…ó…óo ha…óataa on …óum. Anndon mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen, …ìe timminirante njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin √ëalnde Darngal, ko aldaa e limaneede maa etaneede, …óuu…ói fan…ói."